\<\!\-\- Material form register \-\-\>
\<mdb\-card class\="register\-box"\>

 \<mdb\-card\-header class\="info\-color white\-text text\-center py\-4"\>
 \<h5\>
 \<strong\>Sign up\</strong\>
 \</h5\>
 \</mdb\-card\-header\>

 \<\!\-\-Card content\-\-\>
 \<mdb\-card\-body class\="px\-lg\-5 pt\-0"\>

 \<\!\-\- Form \-\-\>
 \<form class\="text\-center" style\="color\: \#757575\;"\>

 \<div class\="form\-row"\>
 \<div class\="col"\>
 \<\!\-\- First name \-\-\>
 \<div class\="md\-form"\>
 \<input type\="text" id\="materialRegisterFormFirstName" class\="form\-control" mdbInputDirective\>
 \<label for\="materialRegisterFormFirstName"\>First name\</label\>
 \</div\>
 \</div\>
 \<div class\="col"\>
 \<\!\-\- Last name \-\-\>
 \<div class\="md\-form"\>
 \<input type\="email" id\="materialRegisterFormLastName" class\="form\-control" mdbInputDirective\>
 \<label for\="materialRegisterFormLastName"\>Last name\</label\>
 \</div\>
 \</div\>
 \</div\>

 \<\!\-\- E\-mail \-\-\>
 \<div class\="md\-form mt\-0"\>
 \<input type\="email" id\="materialRegisterFormEmail" class\="form\-control" mdbInputDirective\>
 \<label for\="materialRegisterFormEmail"\>E\-mail\</label\>
 \</div\>

 \<\!\-\- Password \-\-\>
 \<div class\="md\-form"\>
 \<input type\="password" id\="materialRegisterFormPassword" class\="form\-control"
 aria\-describedby\="materialRegisterFormPasswordHelpBlock"
 mdbInputDirective\>
 \<label for\="materialRegisterFormPassword"\>Password\</label\>

 \</div\>
 \<div class\="md\-form"\>
 \<input type\="password" class\="form\-control" aria\-describedby\="materialRegisterFormPasswordHelpBlock"
 mdbInputDirective\>
 \<label for\="materialRegisterFormPassword"\>Confirm Password\</label\>
 \</div\>
 \<small id\="materialRegisterFormPasswordHelpBlock" class\="form\-text text\-muted mb\-4"\>
 At least 8 characters and 1 digit
 \</small\>

 \<div class\="md\-form"\>
 \<label for\="materialRegisterFormDate"\>Date\</label\>
 \<input type\="date" id\="materialRegisterFormDate" class\="form\-control" mdbInputDirective\>

 \</div\>

 \<\!\-\- Sign up button \-\-\>
 \<button mdbBtn color\="info" outline\="true" rounded\="true" block\="true" class\="my\-4 waves\-effect z\-depth\-0"
 mdbWavesEffect
 type\="submit" \(click\)\="register\(\)"\>Sign in
 \</button\>

 \<\!\-\- Social register \-\-\>
 \<p\>or sign up with\:\</p\>

 \<a type\="button" class\="light\-blue\-text mx\-2"\>
 \<mdb\-icon icon\="facebook"\>\</mdb\-icon\>
 \</a\>
 \<a type\="button" class\="light\-blue\-text mx\-2"\>
 \<mdb\-icon icon\="google"\>\</mdb\-icon\>
 \</a\>

 \<hr\>

 \<\!\-\- Terms of service \-\-\>
 \<p\>By clicking
 \<em\>Sign up\</em\> you agree to our
 \<a href\="" target\="_blank"\>terms of service\</a\> and
 \<a href\="" target\="_blank"\>terms of service\</a\>\. \</p\>

 \</form\>

 \</mdb\-card\-body\>

\</mdb\-card\>
